{"type": "article", "id": 39623, "title": "这个游戏套装，想考考你对字体的知识储备｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-04-09T23:03:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 3133, "name": "Jil Sander"}, {"id": 39339, "name": "COCHAE"}, {"id": 38315, "name": "Goods & Services"}, {"id": 39340, "name": "大與"}, {"id": 39341, "name": "Flash Reproductions"}, {"id": 39342, "name": "Jiyoun Kim"}, {"id": 39343, "name": "Kelsey McClellan"}, {"id": 39344, "name": "Michelle Maguire"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 130, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170409224914vfEat1Xn76SHMDBh.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Type-Face by Goods &amp; Services</h3><p>要让一间印刷公司的节日季礼物既让客户惊喜又能传达出公司本身的理念并不是件容易的事，加拿大创意公司 <a href=\"http://www.gsbranding.com/\">Goods &amp; Services</a> 为 Flash Reproductions 想出了一个绝妙的点子——以字体为主题的猜猜看游戏套装 Type-Face。它的玩法和其他类似的猜猜看游戏有些类似，玩家需要戴上一条经过特殊处理的头带，通过向对手提问，猜测这条头带代表的是哪一个字体。然而答案并不是单纯印刷在头带上的，对手必须为头带拍摄一张开启闪光灯功能的照片才能通过浮现的字母确定字体名称。除了 20 条字体头带之外，套装内还有徽章和一本介绍这些字体的指南。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225113NxUnh8LtomWPkzXd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704092251133kAEO5xNYqDlysnQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.443023\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225113cClXg0UBxezPmD4R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666279\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201704092251122hqkB1wK6bMalnsu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.793023\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225112C4xndBspl1iRT9hj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.743023\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Dokkaebi by Jiyoun Kim</h3><p>如果你在韩国首尔旅行时路过当地的<a href=\"http://www.hangangartpark.kr/\">汉江艺术公园</a>，不妨走入松树林，坐在那些树根凳子上歇歇脚。这 24 张和背景融为一体的 Dokkaebi 凳是韩国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.jiyounkim.com/index.html\">Jiyoun Kim</a> 为市政府发起的一项艺术装置征集而设计的，不锈钢制成的圆柱体表面都经过了精心的抛光，顶部还采用了八种渐变色以对应不同季节的松树林。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225142ofDQ6UHSidG4eZtC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225143zGLX08ui9xnjPBmC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225143WTzZL2yUolRri3dv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662592\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225143Yl2azGMkVg7XRZxj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225142Q4hLD62fOTv3MWwH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706601\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Objectextile by nendo &amp; Jil Sander</h3><p>在今年米兰设计周上，日本设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/\">nendo</a> 和主打极简风格的德国时装品牌 <a href=\"http://www.jilsander.com/\">Jil Sander</a> 联手推出了一个名为 Objectextile 的系列，以一种独特的方式分解并重新定义了图案是如何成型并最终演变为产品织物的。现场的每一条布料都对应了一个作为其灵感来源的立方体框架，所有的图案都是其内置的纯白色物体在特定的角度下所呈现的，比如由悬挂着的圆锥体组成的波点、扁平的长条构成的条纹、由堆叠在一起的方块构成的黑白像素格子等等，让人重新思考图案的诞生过程。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225053WkSoJsOaGjDbHKMv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.622250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225053TPOGL2xFeUHKm7nY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.846024\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225052vspJXygdMkB0PTKZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.067682\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225053zI12p7KVFjhLokUD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.116751\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Coin Artwork by hitohito</h3><p>1914 年创立于日本滋贺县的和式蜡烛老铺<a href=\"http://warousokudaiyo.com/\">大與</a>最近准备让蜡烛也能成为充满趣味的日常小物，以“火与人”之间的联系为主题创立了名为 hitohito 的新品牌，旗下的第一条产品线就是这套硬币型蜡烛 Coin Artwork。这些蜡烛由硬币般的薄片堆叠而成，大概需要 40 分钟才能完全燃烧完。表面的图案由设计组合 <a href=\"http://www.cochae.com/\">COCHAE</a> 绘制，既有写实且配合东京奥运会的圣火传递，也有取材自神话故事的插图，配合烛芯所在的位置看起来非常有趣。这是它的<a href=\"http://warousokudaiyo.com/2017/03/24/newproduct/\">购买链接</a>，售价从 450 日元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017040922503586fPzj3Ug7iB2bxq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225036Ulv4hsnTm6oSGb8N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225036Q1qYtRPS52LH7XsD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.690000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225036mVdx65S9qWcvXIgH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.634286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225036XjQBVniOKS6ECIvr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.692857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Amphi by N U Y N.</h3><p>在普通的炉子上用平底锅和炒锅可以说游刃有余，但电磁炉和炒锅的匹配度就大打折扣了。最近，韩国设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/NYUN\">N U Y N.</a> 为此构想了这款<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/49291561/Amphi\">概念电磁炉</a>设计，将坚硬的表面替换为能够向下凹的硅胶制同心圆结构，产品名 Amphi 正是取自他所借鉴的圆形剧场（amphi theater）。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225638EyGlbcsIzrVAtpPd.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.300000\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225234Mey845oXRFmsD7QB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225234Tr5fMjF7oiQPOLN4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225244mg3PrtN4J6pMFHn0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225239rTogJM8UI67pRLF5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Wardrobe Snacks by Kelsey McClellan &amp; Michelle Maguire</h3><p>同样是时装摄影，摄影师 <a href=\"http://kelseymcclellan.com/\">Kelsey McClellan</a> 和服饰造型师 <a href=\"http://myohmyoh.com/\">Michelle Maguire</a> 合作推出的这套 <a href=\"http://kelseymcclellan.com/wardrobe-snacks\">Wardrobe Snacks</a> 或许会激起你的食欲。虽然美食和衣物的组合并不稀罕，但 McClellan 和 Maguire 并不仅仅满足于两者间相匹配的颜色，看起来非常舒适、协调的质感也是这套作品让人感到秀色可餐的关键。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225018Wwfc1B7zSC0y3nuN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225017xJW1Ve2KDmPvEbky.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225016wfcloyxhXHW9Y012.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225018CXQDzr6fL1RYt7BA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170409225017IPBRcFXKNgDdfSmr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}